					<p style="font-family: 'Varela Round', sans-serif;">What makes people born on this dates stand apart is their drive for method and structure in their personal life and work. As such, people born on this date have a good sense of concentration and are focussed till the finish an assigned work. Hence many born on this date are naturally driven towards fields that are technical, financial or scientific. In fact, it is these fields that make them best utilise their strengths and be successful.</p>

					<p style="font-family: 'Varela Round', sans-serif;">The other trait people born on this date show is their perseverance, however, this is at a cost of being driven towards a materialistic life and acquiring wealth. Further, this drive is generally limited to what they can see and measure. Hence, born on this date makes them averse to taking risks, limiting their potential to see the larger picture or vision. </p>

